title: WASTELAND.2.Incl.Update.1-7.FULL.Repack-3DM
description:
WASTELAND 2 Early access version (beta). 

Including all updates up to 02/25/2014 (build #34119)

1. Unpack
2. Play
3. Like it? - Buy it!

Search official game blog or forums for patch notes. Changes made by those updates are huge and won't fit in tpb's description window :)
Don't forget - this is still "Early access version" aka "beta". If you don't wanna ruin your experience - wait for official release, which will be in summer-autumn of 2014.
